\par Version 2.0, August 2, 1996
\par }\pard \widctlpar {\f4\cf2\lang1033 
\par }{\b\f4\lang1033 
\par }{\b\scaps\f4\fs22\lang1033 Introduction
\par }{\f4\lang1033 
X-Files - The Theme v2.0 is an X-Files desktop theme designed for Microsoft Plus! for Microsoft Windows 95. This theme includes an animated startup logo, special shutdown and turn-off logos, desktop icons (including a "purity control" recycle bin icon), m
ouse cursors, "I want to believe" poster based wallpaper, an old typewriter font, quality system sounds and an excellent screensaver to give your desktop an X-Files look and sound!
\par }{\b\f4\lang1033 
\par 
\par }{\b\scaps\f4\fs22\lang1033 Requirements
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\f1\fs20 \'b7\tab}}\pard \fi-283\li283\widctlpar{\*\pn \pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnstart1\pnindent283\pnhang{\pntxtb \'b7}}{\f4\lang1033 A computer running Microsoft Windows 95.
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\f1\fs20 \'b7\tab}Microsoft Plus! for Windows 95.
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\f1\fs20 \'b7\tab}An unzip program with long filename capabilities. I recommend using WinZip from Niko Mak Computing, version 6.0 for Windows 95 or newer. If you don\rquote 
t have WinZip or if you have an older version you can download an update or evaluation version from their web site at <http://www.winzip.com/>.
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\f1\fs20 \'b7\tab}
The Visual Basic 3.0 Runtime Library (vbrun300.dll) must be present in your System folder for the screensaver to work. Because this file is required by a lot of programs you probably already have it and therefore it is not included in the theme. If you do
n\rquote t have it you can download this file from a Windows software archive like the Coast to Coast Software Repository at <http://www.coast.net/SimTel/>.
\par }\pard \widctlpar {\f4\lang1033 
\par }{\b\f4\lang1033 
\par }{\b\scaps\f4\fs22\lang1033 Recommended
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\f1\fs20 \'b7\tab}}\pard \fi-283\li283\widctlpar{\*\pn \pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnstart1\pnindent283\pnhang{\pntxtb \'b7}}{\f4\lang1033 A screen resolution of  800x600 pixels or better
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\f1\fs20 \'b7\tab}A screen operating in high color (16 bit) mode or better.
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\f1\fs20 \'b7\tab}If you have a high color or true color display, install the \ldblquote Visual Enhancements\rdblquote  from Microsoft Plus! and turn on the \ldblquote Show icons using all possible colors\rdblquote 
 option on the Plus! tab from \ldblquote Display Properties\rdblquote . This will display the much better looking 256 color versions of the theme\rquote s icons.
\par }\pard \widctlpar {\f4\lang1033 
\par 
\par }\pard \widctlpar\tx4111\tqr\tx9639 {\b\scaps\f4\fs22\lang1033 Installation}{\scaps\f4\fs22\lang1033 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs20 1.\tab}}\pard \fi-283\li283\widctlpar{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent283\pnhang{\pntxta .}}{\f4\lang1033 
Unzip the archive to a temporary location with an unzip program that supports long filenames using the directory and folder informat
ion that is stored in the archive. You should now have one folder and eleven files. If you have a lot of files but no folder you should refer to your unzip program\rquote 
s documentation to find out how to turn on unzipping with directory and folder information.
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs20 2.\tab}Run the theme\rquote s installation script \ldblquote }{\i\f4\lang1033 Installation Script.bat}{\f4\lang1033 \rdblquote  by double clicking on it.
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\fs20 3.\tab}Remove the temporary files.
\par }\pard \widctlpar {\f4\lang1033 
\par 
